Commentary Text: Behrendorff to Gayle, out Caught by Krunal Pandya!! Behrendorff's got Gayle, or maybe the Mumbai heat has. This is the exact kind of delivery that was disappearing earlier in the night when the Jamaican got stuck into Behrendorff. But after a brief delay where he was attended by the physio, Gayle - even Gayle - fails to find the strength to clear deep midwicket. It's right in the slot for him, but he drags it off the inside half to Krunal Pandya. Gayle c Krunal Pandya b Behrendorff 63(36) [4s-3 6s-7]
